# Normalisasi line-ending: simpan semua teks sebagai LF di repo.
# Mencegah "perubahan palsu" CRLF<->LF antar mesin (Windows/Linux/Mac).
* text=auto eol=lf

# File biner — jangan diutak-atik line-ending-nya.
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.webp binary
*.pdf binary
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary
*.ttf binary
*.eot binary
*.zip binary
